<div id="tcContentFullsize">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10 offset1 margin-bottom">
                <article>
                    <div class="module articleBody">
                        <section>
                            <h2 class="h2-large margin-top-large text-center">
                            App for tablets and smartphones. Use all of TimoCom on the go</h2>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                    <div class="module articleBody">
                        <section>
                            <p class="intro-large margin-top text-center">
                                Access Europe's biggest transport platform at any time and wherever you are. It is simple: Download the TimoCom transport barometer app&nbsp;– it is your mobile access point to all of your contracted TimoCom products! Whether it is the <a title="The market leader among Europe's vehicle and freight exchanges" href="/The-Freight-Exchange/Transport-exchange">transport exchange</a>, the <a title="The platform for Europe-wide transport tenders" href="/Tendering-systems">tendering platform</a>, the <a title="The powerful route calculation and tracking solution" href="/Tracking/Vehicle-localisation">tracking platform</a>, the&nbsp;<a title="Europe's largest warehousing exchange" href="/The-Freight-Exchange/Warehousing-exchange">warehousing exchange</a> or the&nbsp;<a title="The online European business directory" href="/Transport-platform/Business-directory">business directory</a> – with this app you have a mobile access to your TimoCom Account and can plan your schedule anywhere.*
                            </p>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span8 offset3">
