    <div class="fullsize-bg fullsize-twilight padding-top padding-bottom">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <article>
                <div class="span8 offset2">
                    <div class="module articleBody">
                        <section>
                            <h2 class="h2-large text-center text-white margin-bottom">Omnipresent and always active</h2>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <div class="row-fluid">
                <article>
                    <div class="span10 offset1">
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <section>
                                <div class="span5">
                                    <img class="img-responsive hidden-phone" title="Omnipresent and always active - TimoCom transport barometer" src="/STATIC/binary/900000/images/en/Omnipresent-and-always-active-TimoCom-transport-barometer.jpg" alt="Use all of TimoCom mobile - transport barometer app">
                                </div>
                                <div class="span7">
                                    <p class="copy-large text-white">The mobile access is integrated into the transport barometer app. Therefore, the current market data of the European road transport industry is available to all users. On the spot price negotiations are dealt with better. With TimoCom mobile you are ready for everything at any time and wherever you are&nbsp;– the next business opportunity lays in your hand and is only a click away.</p>
                                    <p class="text-white"><small>* For use on a mobile device a stationary PC must be registered. Any additional device requires a separate TimoCom Account.</small></p>
                                </div>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div> 
    </div>
    <div class="fullsize-bg">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row-fluid">
                <article>
                    <div class="span8 offset2">
                        <div class="module articleBody">
                            <section>
                                <h2 class="h2-large text-center margin-top-large">TimoCom's transport barometer</h2>
                                <p class="copy-large text-center">Das Transportbarometer stellt die aktuelle The transport barometer displays the current freight and vehicle supply and demand within the European road transport market. This means it is a reflection of the current situation within the European transport and logistics sector. With its help planners can evaluate what the actual freight and vehicle situation is in other countries from their office. Thus, companies can react better to price fluctuations and better plan their scheduling. Thanks to the value of information provided, the transport barometer serves as a powerful tool for determining market price.</p> 
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="row-fluid">
                <article>
                    <div class="span6 offset3">
                        <div class="module articleBody">
                            <section>
                                <img class="img-responsive margin-top-small margin-bottom-small" title="TimoCom's transport barometer - the handy tool for a better perspective and more transparency" src="/STATIC/binary/900000/images/en/Have-a-look-at-the-TimoCom-transport-barometer-here.png" alt="TimoCom's transport barometer - the handy tool for a better perspective and more transparency">
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="row-fluid">
                <article>
                    <div class="span8 offset2">
                        <div class="module articleBody margin-bottom-large">
                            <section>
                                    <h2 class="h2-large text-center">How the data is compiled</h2>
                                    <p class="copy-large text-center">TimoCom, as market leader among the European freight and vehicle exchanges, makes a wide variety of data available every second.&nbsp;The up to 750,000 daily published freight and vehicle offers in TC Truck&amp;Cargo® from over 127,000 users are evaluated for the transport barometer and reflected in near to real-time.</p>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
